---
title: Hearty Beef & Mozzarella Lasagne with Leek Béchamel
description: When the weather cools down, the layers come on and the mozzarella cheese makes the best cheesy layer to a beef and leek filled lasagne. Bundle up your lasagne with flavour and cheese until your tastebuds are warm and cosy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-pork-mozzarella-lasagne-35fc1cbb.jpg
